WEBVTT

00:03:59.053 --> 00:04:03.246
at one of the top
urban science labs in the world

00:04:03.270 --> 00:04:05.923
to drive carrots around
in her mom's Acura?

00:04:05.947 --> 00:04:07.687
(Laughter)

00:04:08.241 --> 00:04:09.437
It's a great car.

00:04:10.496 --> 00:04:13.260
Because I believe
that the story of local food

00:04:13.284 --> 00:04:16.776
needs to be understood, told and elevated,

00:04:16.800 --> 00:04:17.951
and in many ways,

00:04:17.975 --> 00:04:21.755
I think that nerds like us
are really uniquely poised to tell it.

00:04:22.304 --> 00:04:23.834
So where are we starting?

00:04:23.858 --> 00:04:25.361
What's our starting point?

00:04:25.775 --> 00:04:30.268
The current national food system
is optimized for one thing only,